{"id":233010117,"title":"推薦美劇《This is us》","content":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/cf523b4c-21aa-42f7-80d8-fe567f5ffe49/full.jpeg\nThis is us 真的是一部後勁很強的影集\n剛追完第一季和第二季  \n有看的人應該知道看第二季的心情 嗚嗚 \nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/dc538f6f-c156-4155-9d30-fd4fe2224574/full.jpeg\n這是一個家庭的故事。\n這齣劇敘事的方式，並非依照時間的開展，用過去和現在穿插展現了每個角色各自的困境、掙扎、認同與和解。 \n沒有勾心鬥角、權謀陷害，毫無暴力血腥、性愛煽情，在笑淚交織的節奏間，回味生命中的圓滿和遺憾。\n\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/e3af7683-9c62-4a54-bd9d-074d4b976434/1280.jpeg\n裡面我最喜歡的角色絕對是聖父Jake🥺\n沒有人天生會做父母，Jack這樣一位磕磕絆絆成長起來的爸爸，他用心付出的愛和努力，是不完美中最完美的爸爸和丈夫，真的讓我羨慕有這種好老公 ⋯⋯ （而且真的有夠帥⋯⋯）\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/97d89eca-ea32-40b1-a9b8-d941db83f24b/1280.jpeg\n\n非常非常的推薦\n我個人認為  是一部拍的很細膩的影集 \n能把劇情悲傷的部分處理的如此溫柔 \n還有裡面的配樂 每看完一集就會在我腦海中打轉⋯⋯🤍","excerpt":"This is us 真的是一部後勁很強的影集，剛追完第一季和第二季，有看的人應該知道看第二季的心情 嗚嗚，這是一個家庭的故事。這齣劇敘事的方式，並非依照時間的開展，用過去和現在穿插展現了每個角色各自","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"28e79ba0-8ded-4acc-a6b2-f015bdef7605","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-02-03T15:02:26.791Z","updatedAt":"2020-02-04T03:24:00.200Z","commentCount":1,"likeCount":15,"tags":[],"topics":["美劇","歐美影劇","觀後感"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"歐美影集","forumAlias":"ea_series","school":"YHC99","department":"mandy0611","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":15}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/cf523b4c-21aa-42f7-80d8-fe567f5ffe49/full.jpeg"},{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/dc538f6f-c156-4155-9d30-fd4fe2224574/full.jpeg"},{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/e3af7683-9c62-4a54-bd9d-074d4b976434/1280.jpeg"},{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/97d89eca-ea32-40b1-a9b8-d941db83f24b/1280.jpeg"}],"reportReas